Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.46,0:02:10.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you hear? Kitada{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} from Class C got dumped again!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.01,0:02:11.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, isn't that Mouri?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.76,0:02:15.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ran! Going home already?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.13,0:02:17.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Sonoko! Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.76,0:02:23.37,Dialogue,,10,10,0,,I was thinking about cooking something good for Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}. He hasn't been eating any dinner lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.26,0:02:28.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A beautiful young schoolgirl like you shouldn't be thinking about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.51,0:02:30.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Suzuki, you could learn something from her!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.24,0:02:31.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.36,0:02:34.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then I'll head home too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.42,0:02:37.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to get my bag, so wait for me by the shoe lockers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.19,0:02:39.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.53,0:02:54.05,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Don't tell me this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.05,0:02:56.18,Signs,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.68,0:02:55.40,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.98,0:03:04.93,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'd better open it at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.83,0:03:06.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks for waiting, Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.23,0:03:10.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.00,0:03:14.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To Ran Mouri.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.43,0:03:16.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S.H.?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.32,0:03:18.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey Ran, it's a...
Comment: 0,0:03:18.41,0:03:19.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shhh,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.04,0:03:21.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I found it in my shoes locker.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.63,0:03:22.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.99,0:03:24.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What should you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.72,0:03:26.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.71,0:03:27.75,Signs,,0,0,0,,A LOVE LETTER TO RAN
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.75,0:03:27.79,Signs,,0,0,0,,A LOVE LETTER TO RAN
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.79,0:03:27.83,Signs,,0,0,0,,A LOVE LETTER TO RAN
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.83,0:03:27.88,Signs,,0,0,0,,A LOVE LETTER TO RAN
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.88,0:03:27.92,Signs,,0,0,0,,A LOVE LETTER TO RAN
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.92,0:03:27.96,Signs,,0,0,0,,A LOVE LETTER TO RAN
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.96,0:03:28.00,Signs,,0,0,0,,A LOVE LETTER TO RAN
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.00,0:03:28.04,Signs,,0,0,0,,A LOVE LETTER TO RAN
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.04,0:03:28.08,Signs,,0,0,0,,A LOVE LETTER TO RAN
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.08,0:03:33.71,Signs,,0,0,0,,A LOVE LETTER TO RAN
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.71,0:03:36.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just rip it open already!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.72,0:03:38.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't rush me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.56,0:03:47.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,'Please forgive me for sending you this letter so suddenly.'
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.55,0:03:51.19,Dialogue,,10,10,0,,'Whenever I'm thinking about you, Ran-{\i1}sempai{\i0}, I can feel my heart beating. I can't even sleep at night.'
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.85,0:03:53.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,'I would like to meet you.'
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.47,0:03:58.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,'I'll be waiting for you tomorrow after school, at the fountain in Beika Park.'
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.11,0:04:00.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Congrats, Ran! It's a love letter!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.62,0:04:04.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since he called you 'Ran-{\i1}sempai{\i0}', he has to be a first-year student.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.85,0:04:07.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He doesn't know you already have Shin'ichi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.88,0:04:10.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This has nothing to do with Shin'ichi—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.75,0:04:11.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sheesh!{uso}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.91,0:04:14.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can't even have a simple conversation here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.25,0:04:15.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.24,0:04:18.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go somewhere else!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.44,0:04:19.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, Sonoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.06,0:04:24.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you got a love letter?\NI haven't had any in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.24,0:04:25.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.52,0:04:26.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.40,0:04:29.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me, it's the first time you got one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.59,0:04:31.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.78,0:04:35.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.12,0:04:38.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're always with Shin'ichi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, so nobody sends you any.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.19,0:04:40.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told you this has nothing to do with Shin'ichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.08,0:04:45.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who's that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.53,0:04:49.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't he a former {\i1}kendō{\i0} club member?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.33,0:04:51.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, he's holding a {\i1}shinai{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.18,0:04:54.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But never mind that, focus on the love letter!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.89,0:04:55.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.45,0:04:56.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!{uso}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.65,0:05:02.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, what are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.42,0:05:05.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll go, right? To Beika Park.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.60,0:05:07.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know what I'll do...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.51,0:05:09.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's nothing to think about!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.18,0:05:11.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll go and turn him down in a snap.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.35,0:05:13.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll say you already have a husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.62,0:05:15.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't act like it's somebody else's problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.12,0:05:21.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You really {\i1}do{\i0} look worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.08,0:05:24.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess there's no choice. Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.88,0:05:27.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll turn him down for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.25,0:05:29.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you going to turn down?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.25,0:05:32.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's four-eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.12,0:05:33.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.44,0:05:36.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You look weird, Ran-{\i1}neechan{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.33,0:05:42.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course! She got her very first love letter!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.31,0:05:43.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Love letter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.39,0:05:44.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.76,0:05:46.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,'Oh, my beloved Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r}!'
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.90,0:05:51.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,'I'll hold you close and place a loving kiss on your sweet lips...'
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.16,0:05:52.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's lying, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.77,0:05:54.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It didn't say anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.53,0:05:58.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you really {\i1}did{\i0} get a love letter, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.03,0:05:59.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who was it from?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.39,0:06:01.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you're interested, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.65,0:06:04.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid, why would I be?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.02,0:06:06.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe I {\i1}am{\i0} a bit interested...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.08,0:06:09.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.38,0:06:12.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a first-year student with the initials 'S. H.'.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.08,0:06:13.25,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A first-year student?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.76,0:06:17.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He wants to meet her tomorrow at the fountain in Beika Park after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.88,0:06:19.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's enough, Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.88,0:06:24.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran doesn't know how to handle it, so I'm going to go and turn him down instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.48,0:06:25.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.46,0:06:26.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.42,0:06:32.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.68,0:06:34.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.10,0:06:40.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If something's bothering you, you can talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.87,0:06:44.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her father's the great detective Kogorō Mouri.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.20,0:06:47.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's enough, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}! Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.47,0:06:51.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And her husband's the high school detective Shin'ichi Kudō.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.08,0:06:52.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.40,0:06:57.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know Detective Mouri, and the high-school detective Kudō{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.66,0:06:59.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I used to be a Teitan High student.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.32,0:07:01.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.67,0:07:03.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're second-year students.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.16,0:07:05.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.67,0:07:10.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should talk about it with you, like that boy suggested...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.04,0:07:12.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can, right, Ran-{\i1}neechan{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.68,0:07:15.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, if you don't mind speaking to us...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.98,0:07:17.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll help you, {\i1}Sempai{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.24,0:07:22.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come in! Sorry for the mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.09,0:07:23.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.33,0:07:27.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, he's my husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.80,0:07:29.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He died one year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.62,0:07:31.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.10,0:07:36.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He stayed in the hospital for six months and fought hard, but he couldn't make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.72,0:07:44.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, it seems someone broke into my house while I was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.26,0:07:49.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I went for a walk with Yūto for two hours at around 1 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.13,0:07:52.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I must've forgotten to lock that window.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.67,0:07:58.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, I usually personally hand the rent to the landlord.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.81,0:08:02.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I withdrew some money from the bank this morning and put it in this envelope.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.86,0:08:05.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it seems the money I had in here was taken out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.74,0:08:08.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Taken out?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.43,0:08:11.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it was put back. All the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.07,0:08:15.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So how do you know it was taken away?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.58,0:08:19.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because the money was folded even though you got new notes, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.37,0:08:22.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Exactly. It's a very faint fold though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.16,0:08:23.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.86,0:08:33.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I always leave my diary here too, but it looks like someone's been reading it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.07,0:08:36.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And one more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.84,0:08:41.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The best proof is that someone burnt an incense stick there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.94,0:08:45.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it was still burning when you arrived?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.49,0:08:47.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How much of the stick was left?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.94,0:08:50.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it was about half.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.28,0:08:55.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then the incense stick was lit about 15 minutes before you got back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.19,0:08:57.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, incense sticks usually last about half an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.48,0:08:59.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know a lot, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.30,0:09:02.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.52,0:09:05.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If someone really broke into this house...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.67,0:09:09.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The problem is who broke in and why.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.26,0:09:12.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He read the diary, so isn't he a stalker?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.01,0:09:17.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But except for that diary, it didn't look like anything had been looked through or taken away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.82,0:09:21.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I felt a little bit uncomfortable, so I asked a policeman to come,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.90,0:09:25.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but since nothing was taken,\Nthere wasn't anything to investigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.07,0:09:27.92,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The incense stick...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.92,0:09:29.57,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's the most intriguing part.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.46,0:09:34.51,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Is the culprit one of her acquaintances, or one of her husband's?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.28,0:09:38.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, how did you meet your husband?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.41,0:09:40.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.76,0:09:42.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's really a curious brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.57,0:09:45.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was a classmate of mine in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.52,0:09:50.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we had no feelings for each other back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.51,0:09:55.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After graduating from university, we happened to meet each other in the city and started dating.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.18,0:09:57.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it's not like Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.15,0:09:59.68,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Of course it isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.68,0:10:04.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, you said someone read your diary, but what was written in it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.42,0:10:07.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing special.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.25,0:10:10.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Things like 'working and taking care of a child everyday is tough,'
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.86,0:10:14.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,'but I get some strength when I think about him.' Childish stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.23,0:10:18.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It must be really hard being alone, Yuriko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.46,0:10:23.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, I already thought about committing suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.75,0:10:32.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I have a child, and thought about my late husband who struggled so hard with his illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.61,0:10:34.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't commit suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.07,0:10:39.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, it's not just my husband. There are so many people who want to live but can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.85,0:10:46.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it'd be unforgivable for me to give up my own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.28,0:10:51.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's so sad, I'm shedding tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.96,0:10:56.82,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Maybe the culprit felt the same way we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.66,0:10:59.59,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If that's true, our culprit would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.39,0:11:09.00,Dialogue,,10,10,0,,Hey, I saw on TV that a thief broke into a house and left without stealing anything after{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} chan{\r}ging his mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.38,0:11:13.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was the house of a teacher who'd been kind to him when he was a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.28,0:11:15.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he broke in without knowing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.84,0:11:18.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sempai{\i0}, you wouldn't happen to be a school teacher, would—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.51,0:11:20.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.82,0:11:24.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But even if you weren't their teacher, you could be somebody they know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.78,0:11:27.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,More to the point, you could be somebody special to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.31,0:11:28.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should write a diary, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.67,0:11:33.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And they read said special person's diary...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.35,0:11:38.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A diary that shows so clearly that you're living honestly despite many misfortunes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.41,0:11:43.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see! That's why they didn't take anything and instead just lit an incense stick!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.64,0:11:45.11,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.11,0:11:50.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe he even sent you a love letter during high school!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.67,0:11:54.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop joking, Sonoko! We're being serious here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.08,0:11:56.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm serious too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.08,0:11:57.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you think, {\i1}Sempai{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.64,0:12:02.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, I {\i1}did{\i0} get a love letter once.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.88,0:12:03.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.37,0:12:06.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The January of my third year.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.15,0:12:11.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if it hadn't been for that letter,\N I wouldn't even know his name or face.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.99,0:12:15.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'd never been in the same class at all, from first year to third year.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.39,0:12:22.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But apparently he'd always been admiring me, and I just didn't notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.20,0:12:24.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The king of one-sided love!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.70,0:12:29.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The letter said he wanted to meet me at the fountain in Beika Park.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.97,0:12:32.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.63,0:12:34.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.54,0:12:36.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.42,0:12:42.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hesitated, but I went to tell him my true feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.98,0:12:44.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.56,0:12:48.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,'I'm glad you have those feelings for me,'
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.66,0:12:51.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,'but I can't think of anything other than the entrance exams right now.'
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.31,0:12:55.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After hearing that, he just left without a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.01,0:13:00.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see...{uso}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.35,0:13:01.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.24,0:13:03.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shūhei Nagai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.56,0:13:05.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! This man!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.33,0:13:22.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nagai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} was here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.10,0:13:28.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sempai{\i0}, were you part of the {\i1}kendō{\i0} club?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.16,0:13:31.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I was the manager during my 2nd year.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.66,0:13:34.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As I thought. That settles it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.51,0:13:38.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Most likely, he's the one who broke into your house.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.92,0:13:41.51,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I think so too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.51,0:13:45.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sempai{\i0}, have you heard from him since you graduated?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.41,0:13:49.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, about two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.86,0:13:51.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From one of my husband's friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.11,0:13:55.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I never spoke about him to my husband,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.11,0:13:59.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but he came up in conversation as one of the many other classmates we had at that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.70,0:14:05.04,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He did his best, but he couldn't enter the university he wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.71,0:14:08.89,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And after graduating, he only found a job in a company he didn't like.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.25,0:14:13.33,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}In the end, he quit that company, and it seems he's doing part-time jobs now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.11,0:14:19.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sempai{\i0}, by any{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} chan{\r}ce did you enter a top university just after high school?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.71,0:14:24.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know if I'd call it a top university, but I {\i1}did{\i0} enter the university I wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.71,0:14:27.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew it. I saw through everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.92,0:14:29.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, Sonoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.33,0:14:32.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Want to hear my deduction?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.25,0:14:34.63,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh geez, seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.63,0:14:43.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After meeting Yuriko-{\i1}sempai{\i0} at the Beika Park fountain, Shūhei Nagai didn't forget about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.63,0:14:47.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But feeling inferior to her, who'd entered a top university just after high-school,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.81,0:14:49.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he couldn't bring himself to contact her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.78,0:14:52.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Later, after graduation, as his professional life wasn't any good either,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.81,0:14:54.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he ended up without money.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.92,0:14:58.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As he was already familiar with Beika District, he chose it to commit his theft.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.97,0:15:02.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, he was headed to a rich mansion, probably mine,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.76,0:15:08.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and on the way there, he noticed the window in your house was open.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.03,0:15:12.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He figured out the house was empty, and he...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.79,0:15:21.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then he saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.40,0:15:26.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The woman in the photo was the one he'd fallen in love with in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.81,0:15:31.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He also remembered the man with her as a high school classmate!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.83,0:15:36.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And from the picture on the altar, he realised that the classmate in question had died.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.29,0:15:41.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And while he knew it was wrong, he also read the diary he'd found.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.78,0:15:48.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He found out about how you were doing your best to live on with your son,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.15,0:15:51.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and thought about his classmate who died in his 20s.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.51,0:15:57.96,Dialogue,,10,10,0,,{\fsp-0.3}So he started feeling ashamed of himself, as he was taking advantage of people despite still being healthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.40,0:16:02.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I see Ran put so much effort into her karate practice,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.98,0:16:05.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I sometimes think I should work hard too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.92,0:16:06.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.20,0:16:14.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So Shūhei Nagai decided to redeem himself, and so he put the money back in the envelope,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.71,0:16:21.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,burnt a stick in honour of his late classmate, and left the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.63,0:16:28.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Finally, as he knew he would never come back to this city,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.39,0:16:31.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he went to see the school he graduated from one last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.58,0:16:36.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that just happened to be when the {\i1}kendō{\i0} club was practising.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.00,0:16:44.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Therefore, he remembered Yuriko-{\i1}sempai{\i0} and started reminiscing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.53,0:16:48.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He might be staring at the fountain in Beika Park now even!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.31,0:16:50.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.84,0:16:53.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Amazing, Sonoko-{\i1}neechan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.60,0:16:55.43,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That was almost the same as what I deduced.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.85,0:16:58.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.42,0:17:04.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This Nagai guy who I saw in front of the gymnasium seemed a little bit different than you deduced.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.36,0:17:06.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How should I put this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.46,0:17:08.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He looked rather languished.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.46,0:17:10.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.32,0:17:13.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I still don't know why he was carrying a {\i1}shinai{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.30,0:17:15.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A {\i1}shinai{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.16,0:17:15.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.25,0:17:21.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, was there anything else written in the diary?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.74,0:17:27.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's actually something I didn't tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.01,0:17:34.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About 10 days ago, I was involved in a small accident with a man riding a bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.84,0:17:37.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At that time, he said everything was OK,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.96,0:17:41.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but he came back later saying he couldn't turn his head any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.06,0:17:42.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.54,0:17:45.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told him that I'd pay for his medical fees,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.60,0:17:49.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but he asked for a 'relationship' instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.95,0:17:51.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Quite persistently, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.21,0:17:51.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.62,0:17:58.95,Dialogue,,10,10,0,,{\fsp-1}He seemed like a pretty bad guy, so I was afraid something might happen to my son if I'd rejected him too harshly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.61,0:18:01.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I didn't tell anybody about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.60,0:18:03.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where was he today?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.74,0:18:08.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's on a business trip until tonight, and I don't think he was today's intruder.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.39,0:18:13.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, everything you just told us was written in your diary, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.81,0:18:14.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.16,0:18:17.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And this Nagai guy was carrying a {\i1}shinai{\i0}, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.29,0:18:19.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.09,0:18:26.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.64,0:18:30.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you that girl's boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.86,0:18:31.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.19,0:18:35.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stay away from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.24,0:18:40.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And keep your hands off her kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.36,0:18:43.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? What are you blabbering?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.33,0:18:44.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.48,0:18:49.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.21,0:19:00.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.82,0:19:08.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Had enough yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.63,0:19:09.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stay away...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.28,0:19:12.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stay away...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.05,0:19:15.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stay away from her!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.50,0:19:17.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you sayin'? I can't hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.66,0:19:18.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nagai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.68,0:19:23.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And who the hell are you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.01,0:19:30.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you want, brat?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.09,0:19:31.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.49,0:19:33.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's odd, mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.49,0:19:34.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought you couldn't turn your neck?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.49,0:19:37.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You damn brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.04,0:19:38.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You despicable monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.79,0:19:41.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you want, girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.01,0:19:50.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, mister, it seems you can't turn your neck for real now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.44,0:19:51.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nagai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.63,0:19:56.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Nagai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.41,0:19:57.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.23,0:19:59.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I read your diary...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.49,0:20:02.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's fine, don't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.50,0:20:06.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I wanted to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.54,0:20:09.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,11 years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.03,0:20:12.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,11 years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.98,0:20:16.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was so glad you'd come to the park.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.16,0:20:21.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I never thought you'd come.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.89,0:20:24.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nagai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.14,0:20:33.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've made up my mind. I'll go there by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.92,0:20:39.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I still don't know what I'll say, but I have to tell him how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.09,0:20:43.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I owe him my sincerity for having written that letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.83,0:20:47.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.88,0:22:25.37,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I made it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.31,0:22:30.29,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh, geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.50,0:22:36.18,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ran said she wanted to tell him the truth, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.77,0:22:38.22,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Did she mean about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.16,0:22:46.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.29,0:22:49.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I said I'd wait for you, but you ended up being the one waiting for me, {\i1}Sempai{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.66,0:22:51.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.77,0:22:53.07,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.07,0:22:56.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm a big fan of you, Ran-{\i1}sempai{\i0}, the captain of the karate club!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.91,0:22:57.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.56,0:22:59.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-Thanks.{uso}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.74,0:23:02.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Keep doing your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.20,0:23:03.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.71,0:23:07.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.13,0:23:10.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it wasn't a first-year boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.00,0:23:12.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko! And Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.87,0:23:18.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And here I thought I was gonna hear Ran's true feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.38,0:23:19.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.47,0:23:22.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you're able to grasp women's hearts too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.61,0:23:23.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're amazing, Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.12,0:23:29.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it great?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.95,0:00:36.64,BCPrologue,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,0)}Only the light of deductions can tear apart black shadows and deep darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.64,0:00:38.37,BCPrologue,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}A love letter addressed to Ran Mouri?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.37,0:00:40.38,BCPrologue,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}What will her confused heart decide?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.38,0:00:41.92,BCPrologue,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.92,0:00:44.04,BCPrologue,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:46.34,BCPrologue,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,200)}His name? Detective Conan!
